{"lemma":"دَمِثَةٍ","slug":"دَمِثَةٍ","root":"د.م.ث","root_slug":"د-م-ث","root_link":"/words/roots/د-م-ث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13043","n13048"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%90%D8%AB%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13043","headword_ar":"دمّثهُ","root":"dmv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, A, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tadomiyvN","text_ar":"تَدْمِيثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft and even;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) namely, a place, (T, A, Msb,) or a bed, or place on which to lie: (S:) and (A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he macerated it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a thing,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and mashed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A,) with his hand, (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that it might become soft."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"quote","text":"dam~ivo lijanobika qabola All~ayoli muDoTajaEaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabola Aln~awomi","text_ar":"قَبْلَ النَّوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make soft and even for thy side a bed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place on which to lie, before night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before sleeping;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a prov., meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepare for an event before its happening."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, * A.) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano ka*aba EalaY~a faA_in~amaA","text_ar":"مَنْ كَذَبَ عَلَىَّ فَاـِنَّمَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yudam~ivu majolisahu mina Aln~aAri","text_ar":"يُدَمِّثُ مَجْلِسَهُ مِنَ النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whoso lieth against me, verily"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he will make even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will prepare, his sitting-place in the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Hell"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; a saying of Mohammad. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dm~v AlHadiyva","text_ar":"دمّث الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, A,) inf. n. as above, (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mentioned"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the beginning of"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dam~ivo liY *`lika AlHadiyva Hat~aY A^aToEuna fiY xawoDihi","text_ar":"دَمِّثْ لِى ذٰلِكَ الحَدِيثَ حَتَّى اَطْعُنَ فِى خَوْضِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mention thou to me the beginning of that tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story, in order that I may know the manner thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and how I should enter upon it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that I may push on in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)"}],"source_refs":["T","M","A","Msb","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n13048","headword_ar":"دَمِثَةٌ","root":"dmv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", as a subst.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damivN","text_ar":"دَمِثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (of which, also, it is the fem.,) in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}